## Task 6: CLI Updates — Init Modes, Rebuild, Updated Commands

### Step 1: Update command definitions

Add `--full` to Init, add Rebuild command:

```rust
#[derive(Subcommand)]
enum Commands {
    /// Initialize Corvia (LiteStore by default, --full for SurrealDB+vLLM)
    Init {
        /// Use FullStore: SurrealDB + vLLM (requires Docker)
        #[arg(long)]
        full: bool,
    },

    /// Start the REST API server
    Serve,

    /// Ingest a Git repository
    Ingest {
        path: String,
    },

    /// Search ingested knowledge
    Search {
        query: String,
        #[arg(short, long, default_value = "5")]
        limit: usize,
    },

    /// Show status of Corvia services
    Status,

    /// Run Introspect: self-ingest + self-query validation
    Test {
        #[arg(long)]
        check_only: bool,
        #[arg(long)]
        keep: bool,
        #[arg(long)]
        ci: bool,
    },

    /// Interactive demo: ingest Corvia's own code, then search it
    Demo {
        #[arg(long)]
        keep: bool,
    },

    /// Rebuild LiteStore indexes from knowledge files
    Rebuild,
}
```


### Step 2: Update main() match

```rust
match cli.command {
    Commands::Init { full } => cmd_init(full).await?,
    Commands::Serve => cmd_serve().await?,
    Commands::Ingest { path } => cmd_ingest(&path).await?,
    Commands::Search { query, limit } => cmd_search(&query, limit).await?,
    Commands::Status => cmd_status().await?,
    Commands::Test { check_only, keep, ci } => cmd_test(check_only, keep, ci).await?,
    Commands::Demo { keep } => cmd_demo(keep).await?,
    Commands::Rebuild => cmd_rebuild().await?,
}
```
